                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="2">The target audience is Upper Gen-Z — young adults who are able to make their own
                            decisions about what and where to buy for the first time. With that in mind, I looked to
                            brands across health and beauty which have been really successful in engaging young
                            people.
