                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="2">I was particularly interested in the world of skincare. Led by
                            brands like <em>The Ordinary</em> and <em>Drunk Elephant</em>, we've seen a monumental
                            transformation in how
                            people engage with skincare brands — suddenly, consumers are encouraged to know and care
                            about ingredients lists and have an understanding of what different acids, retinols and
                            serums actually <em>do</em>. The world of dental care has yet to embrace this in a meaningful way,
                            instead being crowded with marketing-speak which doesn't actually appeal to the
                            audience.
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

